\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5.6}{\ignorespaces The likelihood trap on GPT-2 Large. As mean per-token log-probability increases (energy decreases), the 4-gram repetition rate rises and the distinct-2 diversity falls. The highest-likelihood decoding strategies, greedy and beam search, produce the most degenerate text.}}{51}{figure.caption.11}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:trap}{{5.6}{51}{The likelihood trap on GPT-2 Large. As mean per-token log-probability increases (energy decreases), the 4-gram repetition rate rises and the distinct-2 diversity falls. The highest-likelihood decoding strategies, greedy and beam search, produce the most degenerate text}{figure.caption.11}{}}
